pipeline.name: OCV FACE DETECTION (WITH MOG MOTION PREPROCESSOR AND MARKUP) PIPELINE
pipeline.description: Performs MOG motion preprocessing, OpenCV face detection, and markup.

stages.name: MOG MOTION DETECTION PREPROCESSOR TASK
stages.description: Performs MOG motion detection as a preprocessor.

actions.name: MOG MOTION DETECTION PREPROCESSOR ACTION
actions.description: Executes an instance of the MOG motion detection algorithm tuned for pre-processing.

actions.name: OCV FACE DETECTION ACTION
actions.description: Executes the OpenCV face detection algorithm using the default parameters.

stages.name: OCV GENERIC MARKUP TASK
stages.description: Performs object markup in images and videos.

actions.name: OCV GENERIC MARKUP ACTION
actions.description: Marks up all of the objects detected in the given video.
